  "name": "MMAssociation",
  "description": "This contract represents an Association in the MM Project, acting as a whitelist for actions that can only be taken by members Membership is gained by staking a certain amount of MIYI, which can be retrieved by exiting the association. Bad behaviour can be punished by banning an address from the association, making them lose their stake and disabling their access to whitelisted functionality. This contract is upgradeable since more functionality may be added in the future, and also to fit the association creation in one single transaction. See `MMCommunityFactory`. Association contract.",
